customerReviews.reviewText: My kids love these, and there is no added sugar, just the fruit and yogurt.  Price is much better than my local grocery store.
Great for school as a healthy snack. My son loves these.

Earths Best is by far my favorite Organic Brand for my child. From food to diapers and wipes. II love the fruit smoothies for by son and he loves them too. They are a good snack to keep in the diaper bag when you're on the go! All of the flavors are good but his favorite is the apple blueberry.
Don't know how it tastes I don't eat these but my son likes it a lot. Wish it will be sold in cases at a better discount. My son goes through 3 pouches a day.
These product and flavor are stocked and priced better at Ralph's supermarket.
